entries.title: Startups End a Bruising 2022, Stare Down Another Challenging Year
entries.description: Startups had a dismal year in 2022, from plummeting investment to scarce public listings, and data point to a 2023 that could be even more difficult.

entries.title: The Shift to EVs Triggers Biggest Auto-Factory Building Boom in Decades
entries.description: The car industry has earmarked tens of billions for EV projects—much of it directed to the South—with more investment planned.
